---
title: Archive
pageable: true
per_page: 10
---

.row
  .col-md-6
    %h2
      Find Articles by Tags (#{articles.size})
    %ul
      - blog.tags.each do |tag, articles|
        %li= link_to tag, tag_path(tag)
  .col-md-6
    %h2
      Year (#{articles.size})
    %ul
      - blog.articles.group_by {|a| a.date.year }.each do |year, articles|
        %li= link_to year, blog_year_path(year)
